---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Cookie Policy" description="FieldHealth Africa cookie policy — what cookies we use and how to control them.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-white mb-4">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-dashed border-white/15 p-6 text-white/40 text-sm italic mb-8">
      TODO — Paste your full Cookie Policy here. Generate at{' '}
      <a href="https://app.termly.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white/60">termly.io</a>
      {' '}(free plan). Cover: essential cookies (none beyond session), analytics cookies (GA4 — only loaded when GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID env var is set), third-party cookies (Formspree, Paystack on payment pages), how to opt out.
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-white mb-2">Summary</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li>✅ This site works without any cookies for basic browsing and downloads.</li>
          <li>📊 Google Analytics 4 is loaded only if a GA4 measurement ID is configured. It uses cookies to track aggregate page views.</li>
          <li>💳 When you visit a Paystack payment page, Paystack's own cookie policy applies.</li>
          <li>📧 Formspree may set a session cookie when you submit a form.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
